Systemax Inc., down $1.188 at $4.375
</P>
<P>
   The marketer of computer and industrial products said slower
North American sales will result in earnings at or near-break even
compared with the year-ago quarter. In the second-quarter ended
June 30, 1999, it earned 15 cents a share.
</P>
<P>
NASDAQ
CDNow Inc., down $1.093 at $3.188
</P>
<P>
   The Fort Washington, Pa.-based online music retailer said it is
continuing investment and merger talks with several interested
parties. CDNow said that if it receives an offer, the price of the
offer may be below its stock's current price.
</P>
<P>
Qualcomm Inc., down $9.062 at $61.438
</P>
<P>
   Chase H&AMP;Q cut Qualcomm's earnings and revenue estimates for the
fourth quarter and next year. That came just one day after Bear
Stearns &AMP; Co. reduced its expectations for the maker of cell-phone
chips and wireless technology.
</P>
