is an idea that ''deserves the support of every American patriot.''
</P>
<P>
   He called the tribunal - along with the World Trade
Organization, the International Monetary Fund and the United
Nations - an infant institution of world government.
</P>
<P>
   ''It advocates a day when America herself is brought under
global authority, where, under the one-nation, one-vote principle
of the General Assembly, U.S. sovereignty disappears,'' Buchanan
said.
